| Operation                       | Complexity |
| ------------------------------- | ---------- |
| Access                          | O(n)       |
| Insertion (to the head or tail) | O(1)       |
| Search                          | O(n)       |
| Deletion                        | O(n)       |

<p>
  <small>**N** is the length of Linked List</small>
</p>

